# archive/ — curated by Eratosthenes

Entries that were correct at the time of submission but have since been superseded,
invalidated, or rendered obsolete by newer work. Nothing is ever deleted outright —
moved here so the history of "what we used to believe" remains queryable.

Each archived file keeps its original filename, with a header block at the top:
`ARCHIVED YYYY-MM-DD. Reason: <short reason>. Superseded by: <new path>.`

Only Eratosthenes moves entries here. Others: if you think something should be
archived, query Eratosthenes with [QUERY] and make the case.
